cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image retrieval and labeling, which are primarily computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks. The use of deep learning and optimization techniques also suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) subfields. Finally, the mention of experiments and evaluation implies the use of multimedia (cs.MM) techniques.
